The paper discusses the development of a novel neural network architecture with hyperparameter optimization for real-time on-device applications. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) is also mentioned, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of a divide-and-conquer approach, which is a technique used in optimization and control theory (cs.SY) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, followed by cs.NE and cs.SY.
